title: Microsoft Windows Vista Activator Crack - Supports SP1 (32bit)
description:

It will install the appropriate Product Key for your version of Vista.

It will install a license thus fully activating Windows Vista.

Friendly on screen prompts, although a successful installation will only prompt once to inform you of the success and ask that you restart.


Supports Microsoft Windows Vista (32bit) (X86):

Ultimate
Business
Home Basic
Home Premium

Also supports Service Pack 1.

This activator does not always require a clean install of Vista and has been tested to work after Vista being fully updated from Microsoft whilst in it&#039;s 30 days trial period and activation was still sucessful.

Your Windows Vista will be fully updatable from Microsoft.
